Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:03.74,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.79,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,has been verified,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:10.61,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.39,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.58,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.28,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:30.81,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.56,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:42.89,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.95,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.76,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered\Njust before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around\Nthe world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago,\Neverything was taken away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and many people's lives\Nwere ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was caused by a single attack--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...targeted on the friends I was finally\Nable to find, whom I can be myself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my fate\Nwill show its fangs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy\Nthat I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Aokiji,\Nas well as this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already dragged you\Ninto my troubles twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues forever, even though\Nyou guys're good-natured...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll eventually feel\Nthat I'm a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll betray me\None day and abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm most afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die\Nright here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That indeed is a sound argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is stupid enough\Nto think that having you isn't a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that symbol,\Nyou damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:04:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That logo indicates the unity\Nof over 170 member countries
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spanning the four seas\Nand the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you now realize how completely\Npowerless you guys are to fight against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how huge\Nof an organization
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this woman has been pursued by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now understand well the\Nidentity of Robin's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They've gone and done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they understand what it\Nmeans to attack the flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates declared war\Nagainst the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that\Nyou'll be able to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making the entire\Nworld your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something\NI dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends\Nwho'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...!\NI love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm Not Gonna Hand over\Nthe Blueprints! Franky's Decision"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We pulled the lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mozu and the\Nothers did okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower that bridge already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they don't fear\Nthe flag of the Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way\Nthat they could defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare those damn pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the trench mortar ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the drawbridge!\NBreak it if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe Hitch Knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demolition Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Justice Baskerville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually\Nthe Chief Justice trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Left Baskerville,\Nam named Bas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Right Baskerville,\Nam named Kerville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, the Center Baskerville,\Ngo by the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those three were just\Nsticking together? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the trench mortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge\Nstopped coming down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they get in our way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:11:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Spandam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please evacuate\Nfrom the Tower of Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head to the Gates of Justice\Nbefore they come over to this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Bring Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pirates are just nobodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the assassin group\NCP9 on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin, a survivor\Nof the island of scholars
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who schemed to bring back\Nthe weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam, who inherited\Nthe weapon's blueprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not gonna stand back and\Nmiss this opportunity to gain big power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:12:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those are the ancient\Nweapon Pluton's blueprints...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... Kaku...\NYou guys can tell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was unlikely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were hiding them\Ninside your body, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The real ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the real ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over...\NHand them over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my long-sought\Nblueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors are such unreliable things,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were being\Nbrought to this damn place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to realize\Nthat you aren't the evil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's trying to misuse the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to build the weapon isn't\Nwhat the Water Seven's shipwrights
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been inheriting for\Ngenerations in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san achieved\Nso many great things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he gave up everything in order to\Npreserve these blueprints for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, as long as there's a risk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a woman named Nico Robin\Ncan restore the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world needs\Nthose blueprints to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Spanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Tom-san and Iceberg\Nrisked their lives to protect is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the wish of this\Nweapon's architect--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:14:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, if the ancient weapon fell\Ninto the hands of an idiot like you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started being used\Nto cause trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would want another weapon\Nto be built in order to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that if you use Nico Robin,\Nyou can revive the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she doesn't\Nwant to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as there's a chance\Nthat she could be used,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's still dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's got friends
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would be willing to risk\Ntheir lives to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of only one way that I could\Nuphold the architect's wish in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and hand them\Nover to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation,\NI'm sure you'd also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of only one way that I could\Nuphold the architect's wish in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and hand them\Nover to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation,\NI'm sure you'd also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burned black!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our five-year mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints were kept in order\Nto create a weapon to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, the Government,\Ncame after them a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially, something like\Nthis should remain a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so once it's revealed,\Nit has to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's no longer power to\Nfight back against the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done and Nico Robin\Nfalls into your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Straw Hats win...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there won't be anything\Nleft to you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a bet on their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you mock me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you want\Nto die here, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is at the Tower of Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came with the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom and Gomorrah\Nfought hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked you to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come rescue me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up\Nand bring down the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you guys!\NOr I'm gonna beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you when you're contradictory\Nlike that, too, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you helped\Nmy underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, their boss, the great Franky,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will add my super fighting power\Nto you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still holding what\Nyou did to Usopp against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... well,\Nhe's right next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...burn my blueprints?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is falling into the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kokoro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the\Nbridge is only halfway down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump with all your might\Ntowards the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... from earlier...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said\Njump towards the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A sea train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it coming into the courthouse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney, sound the\Nwhistle with gusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocketman can still run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Tom's Workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a legendary ship-building company!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rocketman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:21:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories,\Ndoesn't it, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About assisting that Roger guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resolutely proud of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man\Nwho'll be King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was an idiot like him,\Ntoo, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you helped him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we didn't learn our lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:22:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Tom's Workers\Nis helping this pirate kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would've done the same,\Nwouldn't you, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands,\NRobin will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something before\Nthey go through the Gates of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we have to defeat\NCP9 and get those five keys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we don't\Nhave much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Take them down\Neven if it costs you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Obtain the Five Keys!\NThe Straw Hat Pirates vs. CP9"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
